request.description:
**Emit event:** `createPost`
**Payload:**
```json
{
  "title": "My New Post",
  "content": "This is the post content."
}
```

**Listen for:** `postCreated` (broadcast to all clients)
**Response:**
```json
{
  "message": "post created successfully",
  "post": { "_id": "...", "title": "My New Post", "content": "..." }
}
```

